&gt;&gt;Dylan: Yesterday's film
is very, very simple;

00:06:05.426 --> 00:06:09.966
Two of my friends started throwing
snowballs at two of my other friends.

00:06:10.256 --> 00:06:11.266
&gt;&gt;All right, ready?

00:06:12.036 --> 00:06:13.176
Three, two, one.

