&gt;&gt;Boy 1: Hey, you guys,
eat frozen H2O.

00:06:17.296 --> 00:06:20.416
&gt;&gt;Boy 2: Ha, ha, you fell for it.

00:06:20.416 --> 00:06:23.106
&gt;&gt;Dylan: We usually come up
with better plots than that.

